    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 at the worst-case operating point supports the regulatory submission.",
